Since I've been overly paranoid now...and how I must "copy" Katie...(you know...I'm obsessed with her...ha...jk) But I'm afraid "certain people" who I don't want to read my LJ, I'm making it:
You know the whole thing. If you "want me", comment and I'll most likely add you...ha. So there! (I highly doubt people would come around and want to be my friend...but whatever...this just means to the friends that I have now, YOU MUST LOGIN TO READ! MWAHAHAH!) It's mostly my bitching about my life and ramblings about Anime...Surveys/memes...and just random stuff...fun. *shrug* Oh yea, banner made by me!!! I'm so proud!
